---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Dermal Fillers | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Balanced filler artistry for lips and facial contours. Immediate, natural‑looking lift with tailored technique and careful follow‑up.", "canonical": "/services/dermal-fillers", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default.jpg", "jsonLd": {"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "name": "Dermal Fillers", "description": "Balanced filler artistry for lips and facial contours. Immediate, natural‑looking lift with tailored technique and careful follow‑up.", "areaServed": "Local", "provider": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "D‑Essence Wellness"}, "url": "/services/dermal-fillers"}};
---
<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <section class="hero-split">
    <div class="container py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="md:col-span-7">
          <p class="chip-outline inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs tracking-wide uppercase">Treatment</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mt-3">Dermal Fillers</h1>
          <p class="muted mt-3 text-lg">Restore volume and refine contours (lips, cheeks, chin, jawline) for balanced, modern enhancement.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-3 mt-6">
            <a href="/appointment" class="btn btn-primary">Book consultation</a>
            <a href="tel:+17163038963" class="btn btn-outline">Call clinic</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <div class="card bg-white/5 text-white/90 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Key points</h2>
            <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2"><li class='flex gap-2 items-start'><span class='mt-1'>✓</span><span>Immediate, visible lift</span></li>
<li class='flex gap-2 items-start'><span class='mt-1'>✓</span><span>Hyaluronic acid options are reversible</span></li>
<li class='flex gap-2 items-start'><span class='mt-1'>✓</span><span>Tailored technique: cannula/needle per area</span></li></ul>
            <p class="text-sm mt-4 opacity-80">* Response and longevity vary by individual.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How it works</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-3">Balanced filler artistry for lips and facial contours. Immediate, natural‑looking lift with tailored technique and careful follow‑up.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Step‑by‑step process</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2"><li>Assessment of facial proportions and animation</li>
<li>Product choice and technique selection</li>
<li>Comfort measures; meticulous placement</li>
<li>Review and minor touch‑ups after swelling settles</li></ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 section-muted">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Ideal candidates</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2"><li>Volume loss or contour definition goals</li>
<li>Desire for subtle, harmonious enhancement</li>
<li>Commitment to follow aftercare guidance</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Contraindications</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2"><li>Active cold sores or infection</li>
<li>Autoimmune flares—case‑by‑case assessment</li>
<li>Known allergy to filler components</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border bg-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Risks & side effects</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2"><li>Temporary swelling/bruising</li>
<li>Tenderness for 24–72h</li>
<li>Rare: vascular events—minimized with expert technique</li></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Aftercare</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-3 space-y-2"><li>Cold compresses in short intervals day 1</li>
<li>Avoid pressure/massage unless instructed</li>
<li>Delay strenuous exercise and heat for 24h</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-6 rounded-2xl border">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Results & maintenance</h2>
        <p class="text-neutral-700 mt-3">Most fillers last 6–18 months depending on product, area, and individual metabolism. Subtle refinement is prioritized over volume for volume’s sake.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 section-dark">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Before & After</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <figure class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10">
          <img src="/wwd-juvederm-960.webp" alt="Dermal Fillers before and after (placeholder)" loading="lazy" class="w-full h-auto" />
          <figcaption class="text-sm muted p-3">Example result. Individual outcomes vary.</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-6 bg-white/5">
          <p class="muted">Explore real patient transformations and set realistic expectations for your own journey.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost mt-4" href="/gallery?tag=dermal-fillers">Before &amp; After Gallery</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
